{"tid":543161,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"好驚！有藍光","createTime":"2018-01-28T08:24:07.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-28T18:38:39.000Z","uid":164775,"like":0,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"80730fc9daa2c4f84f5bc99653a9376b57cc70d5","tid":543161,"uid":164775,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-28T08:24:07.000Z","msg":"夜晚大概3,4點去廁所反房既時候，突然系書櫃既鏡見到身後門口位有一團藍色既光。但果陣客廳系息曬燈，望第一眼，我以為系自己未訓醒睇錯，點知望左二，三眼，團藍光種系度。順間個人系醒曬，9衝入房，驚到訓吾著，種要開燈到天光先訓得反。請問團藍光系乜，其實好驚，求各大神解答。"},{"pid":"56f4d89fa17918da5892790585d784eb0238589d","tid":543161,"uid":39012,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-28T08:24:57.000Z","msg":"你覺得有咩人睇得明你講乜"},{"pid":"5392e3b205331a8ebbb41972ee4736b3aa2f9680","tid":543161,"uid":126046,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-28T08:25:03.000Z","msg":"鬼火"},{"pid":"21dbb4ac36bd7848ad788db5741cc921c96e05a0","tid":543161,"uid":37505,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-28T08:25:13.000Z","msg":"有無藍芽headphone之類嘅野？"},{"pid":"20447b02ab3ff8979695de95783012e85e3a4546","tid":543161,"uid":21423,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-28T08:26:06.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"341f97c33e03881fa99f1f2ec635bc00c9733f1f","tid":543161,"uid":9813,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-28T08:28:35.000Z","msg":"吾你老母 系你老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n死返去5p啦屌"},{"pid":"0ca9ad0ed3fddb9083120423676af78607386b00","tid":543161,"uid":164775,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"21dbb4ac36bd7848ad788db5741cc921c96e05a0","tid":543161,"uid":37505,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-28T08:25:13.000Z","msg":"有無藍芽headphone之類嘅野？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-28T17:08:57.000Z","msg":"冇wo🙃"},{"pid":"f09ed728b1ac06e8e9452473c222ad0d413766da","tid":543161,"uid":164775,"like":0,"dislike":8,"score":-8,"quote":{"pid":"341f97c33e03881fa99f1f2ec635bc00c9733f1f","tid":543161